Package flounder.inputs

Contains classes for reading and inputs from the engines input devices.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BaseButton.Command
    Decides whether a certain code is down or not.
    IAxis
    Interface for an axis based input device.
    IButton
    Interface for a binary input device.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseButton
    Base class for typical buttons.
    ButtonAxis
    Axis composed of two buttons.
    CompoundAxis
    Axis composed of multiple other axes.
    CompoundButton
    Handles multiple buttons at once.
    JoystickAxis
    Axis from a joystick.
    JoystickButton
    Handles buttons on a joystick.
    KeyButton
    Handles buttons from a keyboard.
    MouseButton
    Handles buttons on a mouse.
